data.description: Discover the allure of this two-bedroom, two-bathroom gem on the lower level! Tucked away in a prime location, this corner unit occupies a tranquil spot at the far end of the complex, allowing you to savor the peace and seclusion it offers, all while overlooking a spacious greenbelt area. Notable features include two generously sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms, a welcoming living area with a charming fireplace, and a sliding door leading to a partially covered patio, ideal for unwinding. The kitchen boasts a newer built-in microwave and a timeless freestanding upright stove/oven. This property is move-in ready, with brand-new carpet, and new interior paint.  It is situated in a highly desirable neighborhood, making it suitable as a delightful first home, an investment opportunity, or a downsizing option for those seeking a more manageable space. The location is superb, with convenient proximity to shopping, dining, and easy freeway access. The property is being sold AS-IS. Don't let this opportunity pass you by!
